features: ​​ 【Large Capacity】The M&G pencil case is spacious, measuring 240mm in length and 70mm in depth. It easily accommodates almost all stationery items, such as long pencils, sticky notes, rulers, calculators, etc. With a large storage capacity capable of holding about 150 pens, it is ideal for organizing stationery and makeup brushes. The handle makes it easy to carry, suitable for daily use.

​​ 【High Quality】The M&G pencil case is crafted from high-quality waterproof Oxford fabric, ensuring durability and water resistance. It is wear-resistant, equipped with high-quality zippers that are smooth and durable, promising a longer service life.

​​ 【M&G Design】Easy to carry when folded and doesn't take up much space. When unfolded, it can hold more pens. The pencil case features a simple 3-layer compartment design, making items clearly visible for efficient organization.

​​ 【Wide Use】This pencil case is not only an ideal organizer for office supplies but also serves as a versatile travel case, cosmetic bag, tool bag, cell phone bag, and more. It meets your daily storage needs for various necessities and makes for a practical gift for friends or kids.

​​ 【Perfect Gift】The M&G pencil case is available in three colors (Black, Blue, Red). This soft and durable cosmetic bag makes a perfect gift for friends and family on birthdays, Christmas, and other holidays!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Excellent organizer for art tools
reviews.reviewText: I not only store my color pencils in here but also other art tools like pens, ink and erasers. The bag is large, has two main sections and lots of room to organize and store your art tools. You always know where something can be found as well as if you need to get more.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I really like this case with one minor exception. The top zipper opens beautifully and easily and there's lots of storage room for pens and pencils and other drawing supplies. However, the bottom section has a zipper that sticks constantly and I don't use it. Fortunately it's a much smaller space so I'm not losing too much.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars LOVE all the straps and pouches
reviews.reviewText: I have an obsession with pens and colors. So I color-code all my work, use highlighters, markers and colored pens to control my work flow and this allows me to organize them in a compact, organizable way

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars The pencil case that could...
reviews.reviewText: Although this is advertised as a pencil case, but I plan on using it to take on a cruise. It is very roomy and has two zippered compartments. It has plenty of room for power cords, my phone, wireless earbuds, and any other smaller items that I will be taking for the cruise to keep everything together, and to pop into my carry on luggage. I also thought about using it for sewing supplies such as scissors, small pincushion, rotary cutter and other sewing supplies. Another use I envisioned is a makeup case. A lot of room for what I need when I travel. So I guess what I am trying to say is, this case can be used for many uses!

reviews.reviewText: This is a large pencil pouch. Most students will not need something this large even if they have a graphing calculator inside.
